{"tid":1680342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國拒絕中國就美方未履行世貿裁決尋求24億美元制裁","createTime":"2019-10-28T18:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T09:33:33.000Z","uid":125193,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3b0f46160dda39c5ac4ac70c9afcdb5eec7d1278","tid":1680342,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:05:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">世界貿易組織官員表示，美國拒絕中國提出因為美國未有執行世貿裁決而尋求24億美元的報復性制裁，雙方將進入仲裁程序。<br />\n<br />\n世貿組織上訴法官在7月表示，美國未有完全遵守世貿組織一項裁決，若果美方不取消針對來自中國的太陽能板、風電塔和鋼瓶和鋁型材的關稅，可能面臨中方制裁。<br />\n<br />\n有報道表示，案件的爭端可追溯至<span style=\"color: red;\">美國前總統奧巴馬年代</span>，但突顯白宮一直以來對世貿組織的不滿。</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488718-20191029.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488718-20191029.htm&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=568fa6fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488718-20191029.htm&h=20e4d5b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488718-20191029.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5b3de6da69f9fbf2efee32eeca0c89df4c6899e8","tid":1680342,"uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:06:44.000Z","msg":"愈來愈精彩了"},{"pid":"e722b8f08819af12804f7d54cfb4130a281e9165","tid":1680342,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:06:44.000Z","msg":"美國佬：你大我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900627f3b55936a237ee39fd9a9902eebc7d1415","tid":1680342,"uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:07:57.000Z","msg":"好大機會 繼續加關稅"},{"pid":"d0bd52fd2ce5871e1fe5c3d9d595e739cfa95316","tid":1680342,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:08:01.000Z","msg":"誰大誰兇誰正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/no